52 namespace fastrack {

54 
55 class QuadrotorControlBoundBox : public ControlBound<QuadrotorControl> {
56 public:
57  ~QuadrotorControlBoundBox() {}
58  explicit QuadrotorControlBoundBox(const QuadrotorControl &min,
59  const QuadrotorControl &max)
60  : pitch_interval_(min.pitch, max.pitch),
61  roll_interval_(min.roll, max.roll),
62  yaw_rate_interval_(min.yaw_rate, max.yaw_rate),
63  thrust_interval_(min.thrust, max.thrust) {}
64 
65  // Derived classes must be able to check whether a query is inside the
66  // bound.
67  inline bool Contains(const QuadrotorControl &query) const {
68  return pitch_interval_.Contains(query.pitch) &&
69  roll_interval_.Contains(query.roll) &&
70  yaw_rate_interval_.Contains(query.yaw_rate) &&
71  thrust_interval_.Contains(query.thrust);
72  }
73 
74  // Derived classes must be able to compute the projection of a vector
75  // (represented as the templated type) onto the surface of the bound.
76  // NOTE: We will treat this vector as emanating from the natural origin
77  // of the bound so that it constitutes a meaningful direction with respect
78  // to that origin.
79  inline QuadrotorControl
80  ProjectToSurface(const QuadrotorControl &query) const {
81  return QuadrotorControl(pitch_interval_.ProjectToSurface(query.pitch),
82  roll_interval_.ProjectToSurface(query.roll),
83  yaw_rate_interval_.ProjectToSurface(query.yaw_rate),
84  thrust_interval_.ProjectToSurface(query.thrust));
85  }
86 
87 private:
88  // ScalarBoundIntervals for each control variable.
89  const ScalarBoundInterval pitch_interval_;
90  const ScalarBoundInterval roll_interval_;
91  const ScalarBoundInterval yaw_rate_interval_;
92  const ScalarBoundInterval thrust_interval_;
93 }; //\class ControlBound
